      <h2>autonomous agents</h2>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name">ai16z</span>
          <span class="project-stars">$2B market cap</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-desc">the world's first decentralized venture fund managed entirely by autonomous AI agents. a DAO that uses AI agents to execute and optimize trading strategies.</div>
