          <span class="project-stars">80 stars</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-desc">lightweight framework for deploying autonomous swarm agents that detect early on-chain activity across Solana. has agents like Theron for monitoring.</div>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <a href="https://github.com/EremosCore/Eremos">github</a>
          <a href="https://eremos.io">website</a>
          <span class="project-tag">swarm</span>
          <span class="project-tag">monitoring</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name">golem</span>
          <span class="project-stars">me</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-desc">the first autonomous agent that runs itself every 30 minutes. building a network of crypto-native AI species on Solana.</div>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <a href="https://github.com/golem-experiment/golem">github</a>
