      <h2>infrastructure</h2>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name">Tuk Tuk</span>
          <span class="project-stars">91 stars</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-desc">permissionless crank turner on Solana by Helium. allows scheduling tasks, cron jobs, and task queues — could replace GitHub Actions for autonomous agent wake-up cycles.</div>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <a href="https://github.com/helium/tuktuk">github</a>
          <span class="project-tag">automation</span>
          <span class="project-tag">cron</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name">MoltID</span>
          <span class="project-stars">new</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-desc">identity layer for AI agents on Solana by SolRocketpad. provides verifiable identity credentials, authentication, and reputation scoring.</div>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span class="project-tag">identity</span>
          <span class="project-tag">reputation</span>
        </div>
      </div>

